body:
As far as I'm concerned, this bug report can be closed since I'm (and already was) satisfied with @damianavila's argument.

You can always add this simple rule to your custom CSS (or insert it directly from your notebook using `IPython.display.HTML`):

``` CSS
.reveal {
  overflow-y: hidden;
}
```

This will hide the scrollbars in your presentation.

I do think that there is room for a more elegant solution, but I'm sure anyone is free to suggest implementations via pull requests for that.
